            "content": "## ✅ Validation Check\nChecks whether `invoice_number` was successfully extracted. Uses the **is empty** operator, which catches real nulls, undefined values, and empty strings in one condition.\n\n- **True branch** → extraction failed → Slack alert to finance\n- **False branch** → extraction succeeded → file is archived to Google Drive"
